headline: SBA Communications to Report Q4 Earnings: What to Expect?
summary: SBAC to report Q4 results with expected revenue growth, but AFFO per share is seen slipping amid debt and churn pressures.

headline: Lamar's Q4 AFFO Beats Estimates, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: LAMR tops Q4 AFFO estimates as revenues rise 2.8% Y/Y and local and national sales improve. It issues 2026 AFFO guidance.

headline: Crown Castle and AT&T Tumble While Coca-Cola Rises as Dividened Stocks Take a Breather
summary: It’s been a fantastic 2026 for most dividend stocks so far this year, but most dividend-payers took a break last week.
